{
  "stem": "20405.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened then was [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the German start again the same way like they did in Thessaloniki.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was after the Italian capitulated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody in Athens-- even some people, they got away from Thessaloniki and went in Athens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, was the rich people that had the gold coins with them and tipping here and there to be able to reach Athens.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] The last week [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were talking with Dario Gabbai and my brother to go on Friday to give their last presents-- presents.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, many other peoples in Athens, Jewish people, they were going to the synagogue and to give the present at that time, the last Friday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, to go to tell the organization to send us [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It happened at that time in that last Friday, they closed up the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were in there all together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the-- the people who went over there to give the present.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in an hour, maybe, after they close up the streets over there, the German, all the guards of the Germans, they put two guards in front of the closed doors of the synagogue, in and out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought us-- they came all from the school, all the families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came to-- to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put us on the-- on the cars, they had with the families [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took us to the prison of Haidari [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we went to Haidari over there, it was, was our luck the last Friday with Dario.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because was no way the Germans to take us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because we knew about Thessaloniki.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
